improved_metadata.title: Wrapping Shadows
improved_metadata.description: A gritty and intense track depicting a relentless pursuit of ambition amidst hardship and uncertainty. The lyrics paint a picture of someone navigating a challenging environment, fueled by determination and fueled by dreams.
